data.description: Our 'Homes Built With Purpose' vision is to help rediscover affordability in the new home marketplace. The Elliot Cottage from Mission Homes! Located in Berthoud's PrarieStar Community. Here's your chance to pick your interior colors and options! Alley access,  fenced yard and front landscaping included!  Can add a 1-car garage for $14k or a 2-car garage for $22k.  Estimated completion 2nd quarter 2020. Purposefully affordable, local and charitable. This is the heart of Mission Homes.
